00:45:03.810 --> 00:45:25.541
It's a complete plan of action.
So in other words,

00:45:25.541 --> 00:45:35.019
what it does is it specifies
which action I should

00:45:35.019 --> 00:45:46.045
take--let's not make it should
take--let's say will

00:45:46.045 --> 00:45:52.612
take,
at each of i's nodes,

00:45:52.612 --> 00:46:00.113
each of i's decision nodes.
So when you first read this

00:46:00.113 --> 00:46:03.250
definition it seems completely
uninteresting and unproblematic.

00:46:03.250 --> 00:46:07.052
A pure strategy for Player i
just tells you in this game

00:46:07.052 --> 00:46:09.886
